ReturnPolicy.Description: We are happy to accept returns without question. PLEASE contact seller directly prior to returning items - do not use the eBay resolution center for a return. Multiple quantity (4 or more) of one design such as bridesmaid's jewelry, are not returnable. Please order 1 of an item to be certain it is what you need prior to ordering in multiple quantity. If you received free shipping on the item purchased, seller's shipping cost (approximately $3) for each item will be deducted from the return refund to cover the package and shipping expense paid by seller to ship the purchase. Please contact me prior to returning item. Worn items will not be accepted. Shipping for return paid by buyer unless reason for return is seller error. Must be received by seller within 30 days of delivery to buyer (no exceptions). All items must be returned in original form of packaging (gift box and bubble wrap) with a copy of the original invoice. Please be certain to include earrings and necklace if a set was purchased. We charge a 15% restocking fee on returns.  If you have any questions, please call me at 615-904-5468
